                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>I was the slightest in the House -</l>
                    <l>I took the smallest Room - </l>
                    <l>At night, my little Lamp, and Book - </l>
                    <l>And one Geranium - </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>So stationed I could catch<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 the mint</l>
                    <l>That never ceased to fall - </l>
                    <l>And just my Basket - </l>
                    <l>Let me think - I'm sure </l>
                    <l>That this was all - </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>I never spoke - unless addressed -</l>
                    <l>And then, 'twas brief and low - </l>
                    <l>I could not bear to live - aloud - </l>
                    <l>The Racket shamed me so - </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>And if it had not been so far - </l>
                    <l>And any one I knew</l>
                    <l>Were going - I had often thought </l>
                    <l>How noteless - I could die - </l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
